      • put

        ProviderInfoCollection.Builder put(ProviderInfo<?> info)
        Add a new ProviderInfo to the collection. Multiple ProviderInfo objects with the same Provider.Key should not be added.
        Throws:
        MutableObjectException - if info is still mutable.

      • build

        ProviderInfoCollection build(DefaultInfo info)
        Build the ProviderInfoCollection. The DefaultInfo must be specified here.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if a two or more ProviderInfos have the same Provider.Key
        MutableObjectException - if info is still mutable.
